headline: Three Reasons We Are Fans of Yum! Brands (YUM)
summary: Yum! Brands currently trades at $134.16 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a middling return of 3.2%. This is close to the S&P 500’s 7.3% gain during that period.
